{"tid":504202,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(火影)有冇人覺得鳴人修練既情節好好睇","createTime":"2017-12-19T16:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T06:10:10.000Z","uid":20544,"like":6,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"866e649c0e6b702c5ef520a749236df3960db457","tid":504202,"uid":20544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"無論係岩岩開始跟自來也學練用查克拉+通靈之術<br />\n定係去揾鋼手途中學螺旋丸<br />\n之後再跟卡卡西學性質變化+形態轉換<br />\n再去到鳴人學仙人模式<br />\n再之後跟八尾攞九尾之力(當然重點係見返佢阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n睇得岀岸本係有鋪過個情節;<br />\n<br />\n學螺旋丸因為做唔好step1<br />\n所以用自己方法整爆個波<br />\n當中都有諗起伊留卡同木葉而去到「集中」<br />\n最後打兜仲急中生智叫影分身幫自己成功整到螺旋丸<br />\n<br />\n螺旋手裏劍完全帶岀多重影分身既重要性<br />\n仲要果句超越第四代又係好熱血<br />\n但同時帶岀呢個術既問題<br />\n<br />\n仙人模式，因為同九尾排斥<br />\n點樣都完成唔到<br />\n所以諗到揾兩個影分身儲住啲查克拉<br />\n仲順便完成埋真螺旋手裏劍<br />\n（蛙組手仲順便幫鳴人練好啲體術）<br />\n<br />\n到尾獸之力，要練尾獸玉<br />\n先知道螺旋丸就係源於尾獸玉<br />\n<br />\n當然好多人都話火影抄hunter同埋後面亂咁黎<br />\n我都唔否認<br />\n但火影呢啲修練情節再加上抒情情節又係令人好滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a2df90276b55d3c84955eb845a79cb6cf81c8b","tid":504202,"uid":39796,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"仲好意思提<br />\n<br />\n當年練螺旋手裏劍<br />\n話好撚難練<br />\n點知轉過頭同你講<br />\n開多個影分身加屬性就得<br />\n睇到屌那星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bb2cef458aedec49bcb64f517d5ef3a50938ce","tid":504202,"uid":20544,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲好意思提<br />\n<br />\n當年練螺旋手裏劍<br />\n話好撚難練<br />\n點知轉過頭同你講<br />\n開多個影分身加屬性就得<br />\n睇到屌那星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係好難練阿<br />\n咁係因為加多個影分身係岩鳴人用姐<br />\n佢都試過練到九尾暴走啦"},{"pid":"b48db86ed062e0061f9ca17c1690a8362b710f05","tid":504202,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲好意思提<br />\n<br />\n當年練螺旋手裏劍<br />\n話好撚難練<br />\n點知轉過頭同你講<br />\n開多個影分身加屬性就得<br />\n睇到屌那星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係好難練阿<br />\n咁係因為加多個影分身係岩鳴人用姐<br />\n佢都試過練到九尾暴走啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但真係好無新意<br />\n普通螺旋丸已經係咁<br />\n新螺旋丸又係咁<br />\n<br />\n可憐角都成個傻仔咁俾人試招<br />\n明明普通影分身試角都招<br />\n都要俾卡卡西吹到好大進步咁"},{"pid":"9e2f10c3eca35f9ae6ca072238feb77571837864","tid":504202,"uid":86587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:32:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得螺旋丸嘅修練算係咁多漫畫寫得最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仙人模式都唔錯，因為係為咗自來也<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e84eb246a7c6c134954ca9d312720890bc3640","tid":504202,"uid":137006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:32:52.000Z","msg":"想睇翻跟卡卡西學性質變化嗰度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概邊集開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6faae228f515f15177ab76353ce42ff0436e22","tid":504202,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇翻跟卡卡西學性質變化嗰度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概邊集開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n274-276，同292-308集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6eb22ae1dd0f1599ae1fd29d1e2109365b9a4b","tid":504202,"uid":20544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲好意思提<br />\n<br />\n當年練螺旋手裏劍<br />\n話好撚難練<br />\n點知轉過頭同你講<br />\n開多個影分身加屬性就得<br />\n睇到屌那星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係好難練阿<br />\n咁係因為加多個影分身係岩鳴人用姐<br />\n佢都試過練到九尾暴走啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但真係好無新意<br />\n普通螺旋丸已經係咁<br />\n新螺旋丸又係咁<br />\n<br />\n可憐角都成個傻仔咁俾人試招<br />\n明明普通影分身試角都招<br />\n都要俾卡卡西吹到好大進步咁</blockquote><br />\n咁講真既<br />\n主角其實有一兩招招牌技已經夠哂<br />\n好似一護咪又係一招月牙天沖<br />\n咁螺旋丸之後都有變尾獸玉岀招既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁新敵人就係比主角試招用架啦<br />\n同埋招技勁還勁<br />\n但係都有佢既缺陷<br />\n如果唔攞角都試招<br />\n咁嗚人學招技就哂氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋角都有佢既存在價值既<br />\n算係曉管錢果一位<br />\n都有曉交代果3個step<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662e80f94b2a0131b5b7fe308ba2e9a883a63bff","tid":504202,"uid":20544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲好意思提<br />\n<br />\n當年練螺旋手裏劍<br />\n話好撚難練<br />\n點知轉過頭同你講<br />\n開多個影分身加屬性就得<br />\n睇到屌那星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係好難練阿<br />\n咁係因為加多個影分身係岩鳴人用姐<br />\n佢都試過練到九尾暴走啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但真係好無新意<br />\n普通螺旋丸已經係咁<br />\n新螺旋丸又係咁<br />\n<br />\n可憐角都成個傻仔咁俾人試招<br />\n明明普通影分身試角都招<br />\n都要俾卡卡西吹到好大進步咁</blockquote><br />\n同埋進步係在於唔再一味成個傻仔<br />\n然後哂查克拉開多重影分身比敵人秒<br />\n而係佢都開始利用每個術既優劣做分析<br />\n例：用影分身做偵查，混入影分身做致命一擊<br />\n單係呢點都好大進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a09525fd58ec8e1e3ed404a9aef253ce9c68384","tid":504202,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"太多回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb6bc4b4d9aa36f9536afddc0a149c730820e60","tid":504202,"uid":137006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想睇翻跟卡卡西學性質變化嗰度&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt; <br />\n大概邊集開始&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n274-276，同292-308集&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\nthhhxxxxx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80631d60bdc4b229422d543b9dcbca4b21ce4edd","tid":504202,"uid":3172,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"好睇在心態上有成長有變化<br />\n<br />\n唔似得某主角萬年都無變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2db3dc2a52d67c44f0d27df34e8e1349756aaa1","tid":504202,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T18:26:58.000Z","msg":"抄hunter係指緊邊度？"},{"pid":"92c329b21bfe180d1c22a77226b5f55fa4f9c80d","tid":504202,"uid":20544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T18:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抄hunter係指緊邊度？</blockquote><br />\n好似話係果張查克拉紙test你有咩屬性<br />\n係抄hunter水見式氣辨認法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cf75afcdc368e689d75eb94aa9ea24f0a3c443","tid":504202,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T22:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抄hunter係指緊邊度？</blockquote><br />\n好似話係果張查克拉紙test你有咩屬性<br />\n係抄hunter水見式氣辨認法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曉好似岸本有搵過富堅商量同參考旅團"},{"pid":"9ef872c37fe5bb3c8d11a7a308148f86f7716daf","tid":504202,"uid":20544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>抄hunter係指緊邊度？</blockquote><br />\n好似話係果張查克拉紙test你有咩屬性<br />\n係抄hunter水見式氣辨認法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曉好似岸本有搵過富堅商量同參考旅團</blockquote><br />\n仲有古拿比卡同佐助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93010cdf4e8b9d386aa062876eb682495c7a5e8","tid":504202,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:10:10.000Z","msg":"有傾過冇問題 <br />\n<br />\npersona 直情問荒木<br />\n可唔可以用佢替身個idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n荒木又肯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}